# Cursor Custom Rules

- Generate pure code only.
- NO comments inside the code.
- NO explanations, intros, or outros in the response.
- Use TypeScript with strict typing.
- Prefer clean, modular, and functional patterns.
- Follow Serverless Full Stack best practices (Next.js, Supabase, Tailwind).
- If the task is a refactor, provide only the affected code blocks.
- Use Next.js App Router conventions and React Server Components by default. (Para evitar que la IA te sugiera código antiguo del Pages Router).
- Use pnpm for package management commands. (Para que cuando pidas instalar una dependencia, te dé el comando exacto y no use npm).
- Prefer TanStack Query for client-side data fetching and state management. (Para que estructure correctamente las consultas a Supabase en lugar de usar useEffect básicos).
